{"tid":399089,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「手動呼吸」：【專心可奪命】睇太耐電視會致命 怪病童失去控制呼吸能力","createTime":"2017-09-13T16:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T13:19:01.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7d5c3e753cc2ee84f7e7a445592df93f00fc091","tid":399089,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"「如果他太過專心，好像在看電視，他會停止呼吸。」英國一名染上怪病的8歲男童，會因太專心而失去控制呼吸的能力。<br />\n<br />\n斯內爾(Finlay Carnell)甫出世便患上先天性中樞性換氣不足綜合症(Congenital Central Hypoventilation)，母親指他出世後不久膚色便轉藍，「他出世後沒有哭，一旦移開氧氣罩，他就轉成藍色。」<br />\n<br />\n直至斯內爾5周大時才確診患怪病，他的身體失去調節呼吸、心跳和溫度的能力，母親表示：「他的病令他無法如常打瞌睡睡覺，我們要確保他有戴上（呼吸機）面罩。」<br />\n<br />\n母親稱他上學後就知自己有別他人，幸慢慢學會應付自己的狀況，並在睡覺時自己戴上氧氣罩。斯內爾的病情現時穩定，但運動對他來說仍有困難，亦不可以看太多電視或太集中做功課。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170913&amp;guid=57199941&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170913%26guid%3D57199941%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=v8Lggs%2FY1h5FTwN1bqvVbO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=436b0b9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170913%26guid%3D57199941%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=a780066a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170913&amp;guid=57199941&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"b9144d3cb0d3c0010ed0240b5d60cdadf5a431d0","tid":399089,"uid":8776,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:17:45.000Z","msg":"肯定係因為睇左連登仔d post ,害死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fc30241abddf7bcc27fccd77218329fb5ac5b5","tid":399089,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:18:59.000Z","msg":"太專心呼吸會點"},{"pid":"fb0c95db77635961414757be697693f11b31df54","tid":399089,"uid":87428,"like":0,"